## 🔍 Before Committing Checklist
- [ ] No unused imports
- [ ] All async functions properly awaited
- [ ] No ESLint warnings
- [ ] Build passes (`npm run build`)
- [ ] All environment variables checked
- [ ] Proper error handling in API routes
